What was fixed:
CSS Property Error: Fixed z-index: 1000 to zIndex: 1000 (React uses camelCase for style properties).
Component Ordering: Moved the HomeVisualEditor and other sub-components above the main WebsiteContentManager component. In JavaScript, you must define components before you use them in a list or another component.
Tab Content: Fixed the Tabs structure so that the editor content actually appears inside the selected tab.
Conditional Rendering: Ensured that images only try to render if they exist, preventing broken image icons.
